parameters: Kru "Royal Swordsman Kru, reporting back from duty."
シフ1

Chancellor Shif "Hmm... I had almost thought you dead, but can you provide
a satisfactory explanation for your prolonged absence?"

Kru "My deepest apologies for the delayed return. The complexities of the
Sacred Forest proved challenging."
シフ3
Chancellor Shif "Such excuses are insufficient. What of the altar?"
Umi "The altar...?"
シフ6
Chancellor Shif "Hm? And who is this filthy girl?"
Umi "Huh? Filthy?"
Kru (Umi, can you please calm down for now?)

Kru "Yes! This person is a representative of the Kusechi people. The people
of the Sacred Forest have lived quietly under the protection of the god
Kusechirei for ages, but now their chieftain wishes to establish diplomatic
relations."
シフ4

Chancellor Shif "I see... And for what reason did you bring this young girl
instead of the chieftain himself?"

Kru "Yes! This person is to become a priestess of the Kusechi people and
has been appointed as their representative."
シフ9
Chancellor Shif "A priestess! Hey, commoner! Is this true?"
Kru "Yes, there is no mistake."
シフ11
Chancellor Shif "Ho ho..."
Umi (So irritated...)

Kru (Ah... Umi is getting irritated... Can we really negotiate successfully
like this...)
シフ4

Chancellor Shif "Hey, commoner. It was a significant effort. Failing to
find the altar is negligence... but let's leave it at that..."

Kru "I am grateful for your words. So, may I take it that you will consider
establishing relations with the Kusechi people positively...?"

Chancellor Shif "Diplomatic relations? Hahahaha! This is why commoners are
so short-sighted."
Kru "Chancellor Shif?"

Chancellor Shif "What dealings could there possibly be with such
barbarians? Whatever benefits them holds no value for our nation!"
Kru "But that's...!"
Umi "Kru, it's okay. Don't worry. Our village doesn't need this person."
Chancellor Shif "Hm? Did you say something?"
Umi "It's fine. There's nothing to talk about. Umi is going home."
Kru "Umi!"
Kru "Excuse us."
